{
  "stem": "24364.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so on December the 15th, we-- our transport, which consisted of about 300, I think-- I believe 320 people, went by train to Bratislava, where we were slated to get a boat, taking us down the Danube.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were supposed to stay in Bratislava only about three days, four days.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we were accommodated in a sort of hostel or boarding house, which was called the [NON-ENGLISH], which was originally destined for single people.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It was a pretty poor place.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There was not enough room for us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We-- there were enough beds, we had to share a bed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Two girls had to share a bed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But thinking that we were going to leave in a couple of days, you know, made it all bearable.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Unfortunately, the couple of days dragged on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] because of various problems, we stayed in Bratislava for nine months.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And it wasn't very pleasant.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We were guarded by the Hlinka Guard.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Originally, we could not leave the place.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Twice a day, we could go to the yard and meet-- the women were somewhere on the first and second floor.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And the men were downstairs and in the basement.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So the only time we could see them was one hour in the morning, on the-- in the yard, at the yard, on the yard, [LAUGHS] and one hour in the afternoon.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And the worst was that nobody knew how long it was going to take.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We were waiting and waiting and waiting and waiting.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And there was always something that did not work.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "First there were no boats.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Then the winter came, and the Danube was iced, so we couldn't leave.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
